Package org.apache.calcite.tools

Class RelBuilder.Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.tools.RelBuilder.Config
  • Enclosing class:
    RelBuilder
    public static class RelBuilder.Config
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration of RelBuilder.

    It is immutable, and all fields are public.

    Use the DEFAULT instance, or call builder() to create a builder then RelBuilder.ConfigBuilder.build(). You can also use toBuilder() to modify a few properties of an existing Config.
